        "subject": "LU-16405 tests: a reproducer",
        "message": "LU-16405 tests: a reproducer\n\na reproducer for the problem where create/mkdir can result in\na duplicated name.\nthe root cause is in ext4_find_dest_de() which supposes that\nthe caller ensures a correct non-racy check for duplicates -\next4_find_dest_de() doesn't scan the whole block, only upto\na record with free space enough to save the new record.\n\nTest-Parameters: forbuildonly\nSigned-off-by: Alex Zhuravlev <bzzz@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I3fc3a1bef87c7d3c5c9e0983c930a84a58329726\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
